// This is to avaoid TA (The Archive) to ovewrite files being modified externally.  
// It simply moves TA's focus to the omnibar before openning the note in external editor.
// I trigger it by highjaking the `Cmd-Shift-E` shortcut in BetterTouchTool.

tell application "The Archive" to activate
delay 0.1 # adjust to your system response time
tell application "System Events"
	keystroke "l" using {command down} # mose focus to the omnibar
	delay 0.1
	keystroke "e" using {command down, shift down} # open current note in external editor
end tell
